# 🧩 Neural Network for Missing Value Imputation

## 📌 Overview

Used an autoencoder to impute missing values in tabular data.

✔ Reconstruction-based learning  
✔ Artificial masking  
✔ Improved over baseline  

---

## 📂 Dataset

- Dataset: Simulated Missing Value Dataset
- Source: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/kenjee/simulated-missing-value-and-outlier-data

---

## ⚙️ Approach

### 1. Data Preparation

- Created full dataset  
- Artificially masked values  

### 2. Model Architecture

Input Layer  
Dense (128) + ReLU  
Dense (64) + ReLU  
Bottleneck (32)  
Dense (64) + ReLU  
Dense (128) + ReLU  
Output Layer  

---

## 📊 Results

- ~2.8× lower MSE than mean imputation  

---

## 🧠 Key Insights

- ANN learns feature relationships  
- Better than statistical methods  

---

## 🚀 How to Run

pip install tensorflow numpy pandas scikit-learn matplotlib  

python imputation.py  

